content.value:
Can we not have Eat Out To Help Out again please, it's really not safe & also I'm tired of paying tax (and even more projected in future tax increases) to line Wetherspoons' pockets 🙄 

Would prefer my tax goes to the NHS, schools, social care, safe housing, & similar 💜
